{"tid":1853122,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國疾控中心蓄意隱瞞病情用以出學術文章","createTime":"2020-01-30T19:24:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-31T02:03:24.000Z","uid":255402,"like":74,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"3743bd8c31d05164d6534e337f6756367cf377ba","tid":1853122,"uid":255402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T19:24:23.000Z","msg":"今日睇到一篇academic journal paper, 係一班中國疾控中心既科學家寫既, 而佢地做左張圖實證早響一月初就有人傳人既統計數據<br />\n<img src=\"https://assets.matters.news/embed/f633b99a-ed2d-4e85-adcb-cc3ab22b1227.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.matters.news%2Fembed%2Ff633b99a-ed2d-4e85-adcb-cc3ab22b1227.jpeg&h=a79c1cd3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家呢班科學撚就比支那人圍屌, 因為佢地明明知道發生緊咩事, 但係選擇拖到寫完paper交埋先公開數據, 用支那話既講法就係「<em>精致的利已主義者</em>」。支那出paper係有錢賺既, 所以呢班人係為左自己既名氣, 致支那既疫情於不願, 亦唔願意提早公開數據。<br />\n<br />\n厲害了我的國<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://matters.news/@hzuomin/%E6%B5%99%E5%A4%A7%E7%8E%8B%E7%AB%8B%E9%93%AD%E8%B4%A8%E9%97%AE%E5%9B%BD%E5%AE%B6%E7%96%BE%E6%8E%A7%E4%B8%AD%E5%BF%83-%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E7%97%85%E6%AF%92%E4%BA%BA%E4%BC%A0%E4%BA%BA%E8%AF%81%E6%8D%AE%E8%A2%AB%E6%9C%89%E6%84%8F%E9%9A%90%E7%9E%92%E4%BA%86-zdpuAmhgZiWfjsGUWiSrd83LtWWkSkSt2EL3BNkk4BTDG6pb7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmatters.news%2F%40hzuomin%2F%25E6%25B5%2599%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E7%258E%258B%25E7%25AB%258B%25E9%2593%25AD%25E8%25B4%25A8%25E9%2597%25AE%25E5%259B%25BD%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E7%2596%25BE%25E6%258E%25A7%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25BF%2583-%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%2586%25A0%25E7%2597%2585%25E6%25AF%2592%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E4%25BC%25A0%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%25AF%2581%25E6%258D%25AE%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%259C%2589%25E6%2584%258F%25E9%259A%2590%25E7%259E%2592%25E4%25BA%2586-zdpuAmhgZiWfjsGUWiSrd83LtWWkSkSt2EL3BNkk4BTDG6pb7&d=7U4Tv3rjd6zAHDU%2B6Dwik51DrXAeA17tgS6Eh9jzous%3D&h=11c75e01\" target=\"_blank\">https://matters.news/@hzuomin/%E6%B5%99%E5%A4%A7%E7%8E%8B%E7%AB%8B%E9%93%AD%E8%B4%A8%E9%97%AE%E5%9B%BD%E5%AE%B6%E7%96%B